<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>BlendedSkill - Learn by Building</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        :root {
            --bg-primary: #FFFFFF;
            --bg-secondary: #F8FAFC;
            --text-primary: #1E293B;
            --text-secondary: #475569;
            --text-muted: #64748B;
            --brand-primary: #2563EB;
            --brand-hover: #1D4ED8;
            --brand-light: #DBEAFE;
            --border-light: #E2E8F0;
            --shadow-sm: 0 1px 2px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
            --shadow-md: 0 4px 6px -1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1), 0 2px 4px -1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
            --shadow-lg: 0 10px 15px -3px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1), 0 4px 6px -2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;
            background-color: var(--bg-primary);
            color: var(--text-primary);
            line-height: 1.6;
            -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
        }

        /* Navigation */
        nav {
            background-color: var(--bg-primary);
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-light);
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 100;
        }

        .nav-container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 1.25rem 2rem;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .logo {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.75rem;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            color: var(--text-primary);
        }

        .logo-icon {
            width: 40px;
            height: 40px;
            background: var(--brand-primary);
            border-radius: 8px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: white;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 1.25rem;
        }

        .nav-links {
            display: flex;
            gap: 2rem;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .nav-links a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            font-weight: 500;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            transition: color 0.2s;
        }

        .nav-links a:hover {
            color: var(--text-primary);
        }

        .btn {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: all 0.2s;
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .btn-primary {
            background-color: var(--brand-primary);
            color: white;
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
        }

        .btn-primary:hover {
            background-color: var(--brand-hover);
            transform: translateY(-1px);
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
        }

        .btn-secondary {
            background-color: transparent;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            border: 1px solid var(--border-light);
        }

        .btn-secondary:hover {
            background-color: var(--bg-secondary);
            color: var(--text-primary);
        }

        /* Hero Section */
        .hero {
            background-color: var(--bg-primary);
            padding: 6rem 2rem;
            text-align: center;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-light);
        }

        .hero-content {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .hero h1 {
            font-size: 3.5rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            line-height: 1.1;
            color: var(--text-primary);
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            letter-spacing: -0.02em;
        }

        .hero p {
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
            line-height: 1.7;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin-left: auto;
            margin-right: auto;
        }

        .hero-cta {
            display: flex;
            gap: 1rem;
            justify-content: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        /* How it Works Section */
        .how-it-works {
            background-color: var(--bg-secondary);
            padding: 6rem 2rem;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .section-header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 4rem;
        }

        .section-header h2 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--text-primary);
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .section-header p {
            font-size: 1.125rem;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .steps-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
            gap: 2rem;
            margin-top: 3rem;
        }

        .step-card {
            background: var(--bg-primary);
            padding: 2.5rem;
            border-radius: 12px;
            border: 1px solid var(--border-light);
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .step-card:hover {
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            border-color: var(--brand-light);
        }

        .step-number {
            position: absolute;
            top: 1.5rem;
            right: 1.5rem;
            font-size: 3rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--brand-light);
            line-height: 1;
        }

        .step-icon {
            width: 48px;
            height: 48px;
            background: var(--brand-light);
            border-radius: 10px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            color: var(--brand-primary);
            font-size: 1.5rem;
        }

        .step-card h3 {
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--text-primary);
            margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
        }

        .step-card p {
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        /* Study Together Section */
        .study-together {
            background-color: var(--bg-primary);
            padding: 6rem 2rem;
        }

        .split-layout {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 4rem;
            align-items: center;
            max-width: 1000px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .study-content h2 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--text-primary);
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            line-height: 1.2;
        }

        .study-content p {
            font-size: 1.125rem;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            line-height: 1.7;
        }

        .feature-list {
            list-style: none;
            space-y: 1rem;
        }

        .feature-list li {
            display: flex;
            align-items: flex-start;
            gap: 0.75rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            font-size: 1rem;
        }

        .feature-list li::before {
            content: "✓";
            color: var(--brand-primary);
            font-weight: 700;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }

        .study-visual {
            background: var(--bg-secondary);
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 3rem;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            border: 1px solid var(--border-light);
        }

        .community-illustration {
            text-align: center;
        }

        .people-icons {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: -0.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        .avatar {
            width: 64px;
            height: 64px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3B82F6, #2563EB);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: white;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            border: 4px solid var(--bg-secondary);
            margin-left: -0.5rem;
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
        }

        .avatar:nth-child(2) {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0D9488, #14B8A6);
            z-index: 2;
        }

        .avatar:nth-child(3) {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #7C3AED, #8B5CF6);
        }

        /* CTA Section */
        .cta-section {
            background-color: var(--bg-secondary);
            padding: 6rem 2rem;
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 1px solid var(--border-light);
        }

        .cta-box {
            max-width: 700px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: var(--bg-primary);
            padding: 4rem;
            border-radius: 16px;
            border: 1px solid var(--border-light);
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
        }

        .cta-box h2 {
            font-size: 2rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--text-primary);
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .cta-box p {
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            font-size: 1.125rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }

        /* Footer */
        footer {
            background-color: var(--bg-primary);
            border-top: 1px solid var(--border-light);
            padding: 3rem 2rem;
            text-align: center;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            font-size: 0.875rem;
        }

        /* Mobile Responsive */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .hero h1 {
                font-size: 2.5rem;
            }

            .nav-links {
                display: none;
            }

            .split-layout {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
                gap: 2rem;
            }

            .steps-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }

            .section-header h2,
            .study-content h2 {
                font-size: 2rem;
            }

            .cta-box {
                padding: 2rem;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <!-- Navigation -->
    <nav>
        <div class="nav-container">
            <a href="#" class="logo">
                <div class="logo-icon">B</div>
                <span>BlendedSkill</span>
            </a>
            <div class="nav-links">
                <a href="#how-it-works">How it Works</a>
                <a href="#community">Community</a>
                <a href="#courses" class="btn btn-primary">Explore Courses</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="hero">
        <div class="hero-content">
            <h1>Learn by Building.<br>Not by Watching.</h1>
            <p>Master in-demand skills through hands-on projects and expert feedback. Join professionals who prove their expertise with real-world portfolios, not just certificates.</p>
            <div class="hero-cta">
                <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary">Explore Courses</a>
                <a href="#" class="btn btn-secondary">View Success Stories</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- How it Works Section -->
    <section id="how-it-works" class="how-it-works">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="section-header">
                <h2>How BlendedSkill Works</h2>
                <p>Our proven four-step methodology transforms knowledge into demonstrable skills that employers value. No passive learning—only real outcomes.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="steps-grid">
                <div class="step-card">
                    <div class="step-number">01</div>
                    <div class="step-icon">▶</div>
                    <h3>Learn</h3>
                    <p>Engage with expertly crafted video lessons designed by industry professionals. Each module builds on the last, ensuring comprehensive understanding.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="step-card">
                    <div class="step-number">02</div>
                    <div class="step-icon">✎</div>
                    <h3>Practice</h3>
                    <p>Apply what you've learned through hands-on exercises and module quizzes. Test your knowledge and reinforce key concepts.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="step-card">
                    <div class="step-number">03</div>
                    <div class="step-icon">⚒</div>
                    <h3>Build</h3>
                    <p>Complete a real-world capstone project that demonstrates your mastery. Create actual deliverables you can showcase to employers.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="step-card">
                    <div class="step-number">04</div>
                    <div class="step-icon">✓</div>
                    <h3>Prove</h3>
                    <p>Submit your project for expert review. Receive a verified certificate that includes your project title—a credential employers can trust.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Study Together Section -->
    <section id="community" class="study-together">
        <div class="split-layout">
            <div class="study-content">
                <h2>Study with others.<br>Grow together.</h2>
                <p>Learning alone is hard. Join a community of professionals committed to practical skill-building. Exchange feedback, share resources, and stay accountable.</p>
                <ul class="feature-list">
                    <li>Peer review circles for project feedback</li>
                    <li>Live cohort-based learning groups</li>
                    <li>Direct access to industry mentors</li>
                    <li>Alumni network of hiring managers</li>
                </ul>
                <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary" style="margin-top: 1rem;">Join the Community</a>
            </div>
            <div class="study-visual">
                <div class="community-illustration">
                    <div class="people-icons">
                        <div class="avatar">JD</div>
                        <div class="avatar">SK</div>
                        <div class="avatar">AM</div>
                    </div>
                    <p style="color: var(--text-secondary); font-weight: 500;">2,400+ professionals learning together</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA Section -->
    <section class="cta-section">
        <div class="cta-box">
            <h2>Ready to prove your skills?</h2>
            <p>Stop watching tutorials. Start building your portfolio today with courses designed for real-world application.</p>
            <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary" style="padding: 1rem 2rem; font-size: 1.1rem;">Get Started Now</a>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2024 BlendedSkill. All rights reserved. Built for serious learners.</p>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
